\lim\limits_{n\to \infty}\left(\left(1+\frac1{2n}\right)\left(1+\frac3{2n}\right)\left(1+\frac5{2n}\right)\cdots\left(1+\frac{2n-1}{2n}\right)\right)^{\dfrac1{2n}}
\ln\left[\left(1+\dfrac{1}{2n}\right)\left(1+\frac{3}{2n}\right)\dots\left(1+\frac{2n-1}{2n}\right)\right]^{\dfrac{1}{2n}}=\frac{1}{2n}\sum_{k=1}^n \ln \left( 1+\frac{2k-1}{2n}\right)
